 091: 
 092:     # schedule
 093:     # each time slot has four entries
 094:     # timeslot type - generation type - activity id - facility id
 095:     # for example:
 096:     # (1 - 0 - 1 - 1243) means:
 097:     # routine - graph facility - edu - 1243
 098: 
 099:     # time slot types: (empty, flexible, routine, sleep, transit)
 100:     # empty - for schedule creation and temporary filling
 101:     # flexible - flex time, gets re-generated randomly each week
 102:     # routine - work, edu at this time, is done every day, doesnt change from week to week
 103:     # sleep - fixed, does not change based on any simulation input
 104:     # transit - always before and after facility changes, should be automatically generated
 105: 
 106:
